Languages::chapter
  ::text
    All characters know how to speak Common (Spanish). A dwarf, elf, gnome, half-elf, half-orc, or halfling also speaks a racial language, as appropriate. A character who has an Intelligence bonus at 1st level speaks other languages as well, one extra language per point of Intelligence bonus as a starting character.

  Literacy::section
    ::text
      Any character except a barbarian can read and write all the languages he or she speaks.

